> **Note:** This rule is Windows + Git Bash specific. Remove if using macOS/Linux.

# Environment — Git Bash (MINGW64)

Shell: Git Bash (MINGW64). Working dir: [PROJECT_PATH]

## Paths by tool

| Tool | Format |
|------|--------|
| Write/Read/Edit | [PROJECT_PATH]\path\file.ext (absolute Windows) |
| Bash | relative or [PROJECT_PATH_FORWARD]/ (forward slash) |
| Glob/Grep | relative from repo root |
| Hooks/scripts | $CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/... |

On tool failure: report to user, don't continue.
